function.name: FutureTemperature
function.description: Get the future temperature for a given location and date.

unit.description: Temperature unit. Can be either Celsius or Fahrenheit. Defaults to Celsius.

location_name.description: The name of the location to get the future temperature for.

date.description: The date to get the future temperature for. The format is YYYY-MM-DD.
